Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.51,0:00:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What should I do?!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.52,0:00:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto was trying to get rid of me...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.65,0:00:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and go with Mitsuki to her audition.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:05.81,0:00:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wouldn't let it happen.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After that...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.23,0:00:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I kept them from getting to their destination...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.90,0:00:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and did everything I could to accomplish my mission.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:12.43,0:00:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It went well.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.60,0:00:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}By the time the two finally got there...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...the audition was over...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.45,0:00:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and someone had already been chosen.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, then...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.90,0:00:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.10,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Yes.
