Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.84,0:00:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Wakamatsu Madoka-kun.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.81,0:00:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way...
