Dialogue: 2,0:01:08.50,0:01:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madoka-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.42,0:01:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Over here please!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:16.88,0:01:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:22.10,0:01:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:22.56,0:01:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you running away?!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:26.35,0:01:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You really...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry, Ooshige-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.19,0:01:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why didn't you tell me you had throat cancer? {Oh noes, the cat's out of the bag}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.32,0:01:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:44.58,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:45.85,0:01:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways, Dr. Wakaouji...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:47.71,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...let's hurry up and take \NMitsuki-chan to the hospital.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.79,0:01:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-chan... do you mean {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course I do!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This girl isn't the Mitsuki-chan that I know.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:58.43,0:01:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.97,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh no... what should I do...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.97,0:02:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who are you anyways?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's the one and only Mitsuki, of course!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.23,0:02:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Run for it!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.94,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait right there!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:11.65,0:02:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki?!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.99,0:02:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.95,0:02:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It seems like they didn't follow us...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:26.41,0:02:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:27.58,0:02:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're going to realize that {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  and the twelve-year-old me are the same person...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's not going to happen!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:33.75,0:02:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To say you can transform...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A story that is way too far from reality! {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.59,0:02:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't go back to those two now...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't be {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  now...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.43,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.10,0:02:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:54.42,0:02:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't just stare at the ground.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's get our of here.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're a little big, so you'll have to make do.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sometimes... I just want to leave this behind...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and help that girl do what she wants...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's sad, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it'll be impossible to be {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  now...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hurry up, Dr. Wakaouji!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.64,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That girl couldn't have gotten very far yet!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Like I said...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I came to search for Mitsuki-chan, not {\i1}that {\i0} girl.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.06,0:03:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Like I said...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.85,0:03:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That {\i1}is {\i0} her!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I believed you on the phone, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I hadn't seen her yet, so I guess this couldn't have been helped.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways, I'm going to search for Mitsuki-chan by myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Dr. Wakaouji!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.95,0:03:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... I'll search by myself too!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You moron!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.93,0:04:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you spacing out for... that was dangerous!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Now's not the time for you to die yet!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.69,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You...!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't that {\i1}Full Moon{\i0} ?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.78,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She can't be.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no way she'd be in a place like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.83,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What am I supposed to say at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Madam...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Some iced tea...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... aren't you tired from walking?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's all right.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.04,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.90,0:04:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You haven't seen her?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:59.94,0:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.36,0:05:06.03,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where are you, Mitsuki-chan?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.08,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.79,0:05:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Our office is still refraining from commenting on {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How can you still say that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's all, then...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How did this happen?!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At this rate...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...we'll lose everything we had scheduled for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I understand!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll definitely find her before the day's over!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey! That's her manager's car! {start time fixed}
