Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As you can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...a car driven by someone related to {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...has just rushed off from the office.
