Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takeda-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:47.49,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you've met with {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san for your magazine before, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right. {missing}
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She hadn't debuted yet, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she's a very pure and good girl.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That kind of thinking is just naive.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Such pure feelings can't last in show business...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.88,0:06:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe she just gave up and went home.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:06.89,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She sings with true strength from the heart.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To think that it would end this way...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't want to believe it.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It looks like everything has fallen apart. {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My song probably...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...won't be able to reach you now...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where am I?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... I'm inside the lighthouse, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.07,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto... where'd he go off to?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.39,0:07:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The moon pendant Eichi-kun gave me... it's ruined... {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:47.98,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even though I always... always treasured it...
