Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:55.78,Myself TL IN19,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\fad(600,200)}Was it the same for the both of us?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:56.70,0:08:02.87,Myself TL IN19,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\fad(200,200)}Even though I decided to protect you back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:09.38,Myself TL IN19,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\fad(200,200)}Why can't I seal you away in my memories...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:15.43,Myself TL IN19,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\fad(200,200)}You're too far away... too close to me... for me to reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:21.52,Myself TL IN19,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\fad(200,200)}The more I try to forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:28.86,Myself TL IN19,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\fad(200,200)}The more you are in my thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:09:01.56,Myself TL IN19,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\fad(200,200)}Always in tears... I continue to search like a lost child...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:13.86,Myself TL IN19,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\fad(200,200)}But... a thing like eternity... doesn't really exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:25.21,Myself TL IN19,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\fad(200,200)}"It's okay to not trust anyone"... you mumbled...
