Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.14,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}It sounds so... painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.97,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:14.09,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}I'm the only one who can hear Takuto singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.22,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.86,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}It's not just my song...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:24.72,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}All those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.50,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}Even Takuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.02,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:33.21,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}Surely, someday... Eichi-kun will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.87,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.55,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}...really want to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\be1}Well... you see...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.61,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Back in the old days, people used to get up early to catch salmon...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.10,0:11:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...what are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What should I do...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Get on a boat...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and sail off to America, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.74,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you try to sing in America...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you'll get Eichi's attention faster, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}America, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Give up here and go to America...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It might be better there.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.59,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Will we be all right?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My English.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.97,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?!
