Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're best with a smile on your face.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's beautiful...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and Ooshige-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I think I should tell them everything.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After I tell them everything...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.44,0:12:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it can't be helped if they don't forgive me.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I... still want to sing.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You won't be a Shinigami anymore...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.37,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As long as you're doing what you want to...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'll keep on following your dream.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you, Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}S-Stupid... don't just hug me for no reason at all!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:05.26,0:13:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I like your singing, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So you did hear me...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's 'cause...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you're a gentle person...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Someone I can talk to...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're trying to embarrass me again!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's 'cause... it's the truth!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.62,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Saying "Like..." {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.50,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't say that so easily... stupid Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:38.38,0:13:41.80,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Not when the one you like the most... is that Eichi...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.34,Note,,0,0,0,Sign,{\fs40\be1\bord0\shad0\c&H010000&\b0\pos(268.479,242)}Reception Room
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei... Ooshige-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry for causing you so much trouble!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-chan... is your fever gone?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What about your cough?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways... let's go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll call your grandma immediately.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.03,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.70,0:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You need to tell us something?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.66,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Aren't you Mitsuki-chan's little sister, Mikazuki-chan? {Bingo, I was right about the tl error in episode 3, it was fixed at this point}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what you told me when we last met.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.83,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Back then... I was lying.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.07,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.38,0:14:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Th-Then...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who's the {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  I'm always with?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.64,0:14:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's also me.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no way that could be true...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what I came to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:37.73,0:14:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Be strong.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.61,0:14:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.03,0:14:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you remember the day I asked you about the audition?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.12,0:14:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.83,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In reality...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After you left...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...something happened...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...right before my eyes...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.75,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A Shinigami by the name of Takuto appeared.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.92,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He told me that I had just one year left to live...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A Shinigami... and that you have only one year left to live...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That kind of story is...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.60,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's listen to her story a little longer.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please go on.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After I heard that...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:27.28,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I thought that this would be my only chance to audition and become a singer.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.20,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... twelve-year-olds couldn't audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So then... Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.71,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}I get it.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:42.18,0:15:44.59,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be3}This will turn you into a sixteen-year-old.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ever since then...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:53.93,0:15:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I've been able to turn my body into that of the sixteen-year-old {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm the only one who can see Takuto, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.69,0:16:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I know that it's hard for you to just believe what I'm saying...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But if you don't believe me...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.36,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'll never be able to sing as {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  again!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:14.32,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I understand what you're saying, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:16.95,0:16:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...can that all be real?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh well.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If they won't believe your story...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.84,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...we'll just have to show them.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.09,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:33.30,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei... Ooshige-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My story wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please watch closely.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei... Ooshige-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is me as a sixteen-year-old.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:17.51,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:19.18,0:17:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you believe what I say now?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}H-Hey... Mitsuki... {start time fixed}
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is this real?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.41,0:17:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This must be some kind of optical illusion or something, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It happened right before your eyes and you still don't believe her!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.04,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.71,0:17:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is this?!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.79,0:17:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:47.87,0:17:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm the Shinigami, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This isn't how I usually look...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:52.05,0:17:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...but I can only talk to you when I'm in this form.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.88,0:17:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A-Are you really a Shinigami?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We have no choice but to believe it.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks to Takuto-kun's power...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Mitsuki-chan can change into a sixteen-year-old...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.81,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After learning that...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.23,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...everything that's happened since then...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.86,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it all makes sense now.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.19,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...to say that Mitsuki-chan only has one year left...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's the only thing that I can't accept.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Despite that...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We can't allow her to use her throat constantly...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.66,0:18:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But when she's a sixteen year old...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...she's totally healthy.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that true?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way... how can that be...?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:35.13,0:18:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you don't believe it, run a test on her later.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.47,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, Sensei... I want to keep on singing.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.68,0:18:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I beg you!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't let you, Mitsuki-chan...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why?!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.35,0:18:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm running out of time.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In the time that I have left...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I want to keep on singing!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.11,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't waste a second... I want to tell Eichi-kun how I feel!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And then...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.74,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's not it.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.83,0:19:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's not about singing and living.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You sing to live...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You live to sing... {To live is to fight, and to fight is to live}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Dr. Wakaouji.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can't we do something about Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Until Mitsuki's dream comes true...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just until then...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.39,0:19:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm begging you, Wakaouji-sensei!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.73,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-chan...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...can you give me some time?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to think this over.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.03,0:19:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'd like to do as much as I can for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's your life we are talking about here.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:45.08,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,435)}I want to help your dreams come true.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,435)}Dr. Wakaouji seems like a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,435)}Cheer up Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:34.60,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is this okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko's going to leave.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:38.86,0:21:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What... you're not mad at her?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's her fault that you didn't make it to the audition.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's true, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Meroko must have had her reasons.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.34,0:21:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man... how long are you going to keep on trusting people?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.45,0:21:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's none of my business now.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.74,0:21:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If she wants to come back, she can come back on her own.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez, Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Next time on Full Moon wo Sagashite:
Dialogue: 2,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko, Left Alone
Dialogue: 2,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.88,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look forward to it!
